# .dotfiles

My personal dotfiles.

## Prerequisites

1. [git](https://git-scm.com/)
2. [git-lfs](https://git-lfs.com/)

## Installation

```bash
# Clone the repo with ssh
git clone --filter=blob:none git@github.com:zeekcheung/.dotfiles ~/.dotfiles
# Or clone the repo with https
git clone --filter=blob:none https://github.com/zeekcheung/.dotfiles ~/.dotfiles

cd ~/.dotfiles

# Setup git-lfs
git lfs install

# Pull all files from git-lfs
git lfs pull

# Setup the system
./arch # Arch

./arch-wsl # Arch WSL

./windows.ps1 # Windows
```
